{"tid":1577541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急，集思廣益]全民裝Cam有無計？","createTime":"2019-09-17T18:02:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T15:31:59.000Z","uid":70915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"785e5ae66af4a45061ca4ef55b2c1f126c027556","tid":1577541,"uid":70915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T18:02:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">目的：形成一個民間CCTV網路，監察社區安全</span></span><br />\n<br />\nWHY<br />\n幾單被自殺，依家有好多推論無辦法FC到<br />\n除左被滅聲、無人敢行出黎<br />\n更加係因為<span style=\"color: red;\">無片無真相！</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">呢場仗，要人證物證俱在先有勝算！</span><br />\n<br />\n為左保護自己同身邊嘅人，<br />\n同埋有起事上黎可以有系統地<span style=\"color: red;\">重組案情</span><br />\n我地可以學習下RTHK 721果種調查嘅思路<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">成立一個民間CCTV網路</span><br />\n<br />\nHOW<br />\n形式類似一個<span style=\"color: red;\">CCTV資料庫</span>咁，<br />\n你如果願意提供CAM片、支持民間調查嘅<br />\n就留低一d基本資料，例如地區、屋苑等等<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外文宣方面大力宣傳裝cam</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-車主/司機：裝齊d車cam<br />\n-屋企嘅響門口、窗口裝cam<br />\n-拉埋黃店餐廳，攞佢地嘅同意同支持<br />\n<br />\n我知道保密、技術、執行上同法律上<br />\n有好多野未諗得好仔細<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我覺得咁樣等人爆料<br />\n我地係處於被動嘅下風！<br />\n我唔甘心真相就咁石沈大海，<br />\n市民要活於惶恐之中！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">開放俾大家討論，係咪可行</span>"},{"pid":"44b4351b3460aaa7059ba929a0a544b2a81cf309","tid":1577541,"uid":70915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T18:05:42.000Z","msg":"推，我好少開po<br />\n唔想義士犧牲得不明不白<br />\n唔想再俾d死黑警咁無法無天<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b535846101d66a0ed898b7735f4b92ce7a944d1","tid":1577541,"uid":125349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T18:07:46.000Z","msg":"你俾人周到拎走左張卡<br />\n你就會變左被做篤灰...."},{"pid":"940048dcbd8bea816f8fe8f9680352aa3902f424","tid":1577541,"uid":70915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T18:07:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8534ffa72b6c2d84fa97f63e45828732d1b1ce20","tid":1577541,"uid":31623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:31:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}